BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 148.8 610 Td (BLW BASICS EXPLAINED) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 598 m 382 598 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 575 Td (WHAT IS BABY-LED WEANING \(BLW\)?) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 560 Td (Letting your baby self-feed from the start of solids \(around 6) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 545 Td (months\). No purees, no spoon-feeding - baby picks up food!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 530 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 515 Td (BENEFITS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 500 Td (- Develops fine motor skills and hand-eye coordination) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 485 Td (- Baby learns to self-regulate appetite) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 470 Td (- Reduces picky eating \(exposed to textures early\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 455 Td (- Family eats together \(same foods, modified\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 440 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 425 Td (SAFETY ESSENTIALS:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 410 Td (- Baby must sit upright independently) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 395 Td (- Always supervise meals \(never leave baby alone with food\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 380 Td (- Know the difference between gagging and choking) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 365 Td (- Cut round foods \(grapes, cherry tomatoes\) lengthwise) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 350 Td (- No honey until age 1, no whole nuts until age 4) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 335 Td (- Soft enough to squish between your fingers = safe) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 320 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 305 Td (FIRST FOOD SHAPES \(for 6-month-olds\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 290 Td (- Finger-length strips \(baby grabs with whole fist\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 275 Td (- Soft, mashable with gums) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 260 Td (- Examples: avocado strips, banana, steamed sweet potato) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
