BT 0 g /F2 14 Tf 135.36 610 Td (GAGGING vs CHOKING GUIDE) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 50 598 m 382 598 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 575 Td (GAGGING \(NORMAL - do NOT intervene\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 561 Td (- Baby is noisy \(coughing, sputtering\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 547 Td (- Face may turn red briefly) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 533 Td (- Baby can still breathe) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 519 Td (- Baby resolves it on their own) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 505 Td (- This is baby LEARNING to eat safely) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 491 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 477 Td (CHOKING \(EMERGENCY - act immediately\):) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 463 Td (- Baby is SILENT \(no sound\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 449 Td (- Cannot cry or cough) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 435 Td (- Lips/face turning blue) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 421 Td (- Panicked look) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 407 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 393 Td (IF CHOKING: Infant CPR \(take a class BEFORE starting BLW!\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 379 Td (1. 5 back blows \(between shoulder blades\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 365 Td (2. 5 chest thrusts \(center of chest\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 351 Td (3. Alternate until object dislodges or baby goes limp) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 337 Td (4. Call 911 if not resolved) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 323 Td () Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 309 Td (PREVENT CHOKING:) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 295 Td (- No round foods \(cut grapes, hot dogs lengthwise\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 281 Td (- No hard foods \(raw carrot, whole nuts\)) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 267 Td (- Always supervise) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 253 Td (- Baby sitting upright in high chair) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 50 239 Td (- No eating in car seats or while walking) Tj ET

endstream
